        <section id="main"><article id="post-025 23-征四方篇 and 24-王祭篇 #摩诃婆罗多# 札记（脑残粉最高境界是把男神变成真·男神）" class="article article-type-post" itemscope itemprop="blogPost">
  <div class="article-meta">
    <a href="/29ac09_66b0417" class="article-date">
  <time datetime="2015-03-30T19:16:34.000Z" itemprop="datePublished">2015-03-31</time>
</a>
    
